summary: High-energy Manager with experience in building and motivating dynamic teams, fostering a culture of open communication, supervision and training, client relations, and strong attention to detail.

experience.title: Store Manager
experience.description: Managed a team of 10. Opened a new store location and assisted in recruiting and training new staff. Delivered excellent customer service by greeting and assisting each customer. Developed the department's first incentive performance plan, which motivated the team. Resulted in a 23% increase in sales. Team surpassed revenue goals in four consecutive quarters.

experience.title: Store Manager
experience.description: Managed a team of 6. Completed a series of training sessions to advance from Assistant Manager to Store Manager. Directed and supervised employees engaged in sales, inventory-taking and reconciling cash receipts. Initiated program that standardized employee training and led to increase in customer satisfaction by 12%. Addressed customer inquiries and resolved complaints.
